    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an impeccable E92 M3, a masterclass in high-revving, naturally aspirated performance. At its heart lies the S65 4.0L V8 engine, featuring individual throttle bodies and a stratospheric 8,400 RPM redline. This example is paired with a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock for unparalleled cornering dynamics. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), providing adjustable suspension kinematics for varied driving environments. Meticulously preserved, the vehicle shows no signs of subframe fatigue or rod bearing wear, maintaining factory-spec tolerances throughout. The interior remains in showroom condition, with the Novillo leather retaining its original matte texture. A definitive collector-grade specimen for the technical purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
