      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-standard vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, boasting a flawless original finish with zero imperfections, swirl marks, or chips. Inside, the cabin remains in time-capsule condition; the premium leather retains its factory-fresh scent and supple texture, with no visible wear on the bolsters or touchpoints. Every electronic feature and mechanical component functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Accompanied by a comprehensive, folder-thick service history and all original documentation, this is a rare opportunity to own a piece of automotive perfection that looks and drives as if it has never left the dealership floor.",
